<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا لَكُمْ كَيْفَ تَحْكُمُونَ}</span> ... بِئْسَ الحُكْمُ مَا تَحْكُمُونَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلْطَانٌ}</span> ... حُجَّةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْجِنَّةِ}</span> ... المَلَائِكَةِ، سُمُّوا بِذَلِكَ؛ لِاجْتِنَانِهِمْ عَنِ الأَبْصَارِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَسَبًا}</span> ... قَرَابَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمُحْضَرُونَ}</span> ... إِنَّ الكُفَّارَ سَيُحْضَرُونَ لِلْعَذَابِ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... تَنْزِيهًا للهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِفَاتِنِينَ}</span> ... بِمُضِلِّينَ أَحدًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَالِ الْجَحِيمِ}</span> ... مَنْ يَصْلَى الجَحِيمَ بِدُخُولِهَا وَمُقَاسَاةِ حَرِّهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصَّافُّونَ}</span> ... الوَاقِفُونَ صُفُوفًا فِي عِبَادَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُسَبِّحُونَ}</span> ... المُنَزِّهُونَ اللهَ عَنْ كُلِّ مَا لَا يَلِيقُ بِه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِكْرًا مِّنْ الْأَوَّلِينَ}</span> ... كِتَابًا مِنْ كُتُبِ الأَنْبِيَاءِ السَّابِقِينَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
